data.description: This gorgeous 3 bedroom, 3 full baths and 3-car garage Gold Canyon home is practically brand new! This home build was just completed 8 months ago, is barely lived in & is loaded with custom upgrades. Upgrades include sliding wall to back yard, tile flooring in all areas except the bedrooms, 5'' baseboards throughout, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, a walk in pantry and subway tile backsplash & butlers pantry in custom kitchen.  Secondary bedroom has a private full bathroom, and the primary includes 2 walk in closets & an amazing grand bathroom! A multi slide door off of the spacious great room opens to the extended covered patio, grass backyard and pergola sitting area perfect for your BBQ's.
